# SnapAsset AI - Production Environment Variables
#
# IMPORTANT: This is an example file. DO NOT commit actual production values!
# Add these variables to Netlify Dashboard: Site Settings → Environment Variables
#
# Documentation: https://docs.netlify.com/configure-builds/environment-variables/

# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE PRODUCTION
# =============================================================================
# Get these from: https://app.supabase.com/project/YOUR_PROJECT/settings/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-production-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_production_anon_key_here

# =============================================================================
# STRIPE PRODUCTION (LIVE KEYS - NOT TEST KEYS!)
# =============================================================================
# Get these from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_***
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_***

# Get this from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks
# Webhook endpoint: https://snapassetai.com/api/stripe/webhook
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_***

# =============================================================================
# APPLICATION CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://snapassetai.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_ENV=production

# =============================================================================
# EBAY API PRODUCTION (Optional - for valuation features)
# =============================================================================
# Get these from: https://developer.ebay.com/my/keys
EBAY_APP_ID=your_production_app_id
EBAY_CERT_ID=your_production_cert_id
EBAY_DEV_ID=your_production_dev_id

# =============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
#
# Before deploying to production:
#
# 1. Supabase Setup
#    □ Create production Supabase project
#    □ Run all database migrations
#    □ Configure RLS policies
#    □ Set up storage buckets (asset-photos, receipts, appraisal-documents)
#    □ Test authentication flows
#    □ Copy anon key and URL to Netlify
#
# 2. Stripe Setup
#    □ Switch to Live mode in Stripe dashboard
#    □ Copy live publishable and secret keys
#    □ Create webhook endpoint: https://snapassetai.com/api/stripe/webhook
#    □ Subscribe to events: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.*
#    □ Copy webhook secret to Netlify
#    □ Test payment flow in production
#
# 3. Netlify Configuration
#    □ Go to: https://app.netlify.com/sites/snapassetai/settings/deploys#environment
#    □ Add all environment variables above
#    □ Select "Production" deployment context
#    □ Save changes
#
# 4. Domain & DNS
#    □ Configure custom domain (snapassetai.com)
#    □ Enable HTTPS
#    □ Update Supabase redirect URLs
#    □ Update Stripe webhook URLs
#
# 5. Testing
#    □ Build succeeds: npm run build
#    □ All routes accessible
#    □ Auth flows work
#    □ Test payment (small amount, then refund)
#    □ Verify webhook events
#    □ Check error logs
#    □ Mobile responsive
#    □ Lighthouse score > 85
#
# =============================================================================
